{"tid":531513,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《摩登家庭》預計於第十季劇終","createTime":"2018-01-17T02:10:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T06:14:41.000Z","uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f16bdc94e0fc64daba6e86694c1a78750aaeee2b","tid":531513,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T02:10:41.000Z","msg":"曾連續6年獲艾美獎、並得過金球獎最佳劇集（喜劇/歌劇組）嘅皇牌喜劇《摩登家庭》（Modern Family）將於第十季劇終！最近劇集兩位製作人Steve Levitan與Christopher Lloyd接受《The Hollywood Reporter》訪問，指自己「唔能夠想像劇集會於第十季之後發展落去」。Levitan指：「我哋嘅計劃係第十季完結，如果我哋可以於觀眾想要更多嘅時候終結，就係最正確嘅做法。」雖然佢指呢個決定並非100%落實，但似乎亦去意已決。劇集現正播出第9季，並會於聽日播出第200集。"},{"pid":"b1e93784fc3f2d74922b53017049590346793c42","tid":531513,"uid":48791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T02:50:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1671a2418901c05b35fe9e8321329b7132f6fc8","tid":531513,"uid":8532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T02:51:38.000Z","msg":"人物都老喇，小朋友又大哂<br />\n都差唔多要一個完結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff003d0dba6b139b4185800b4ead592d69cf401","tid":531513,"uid":18645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T05:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3f1429470aa9963b9e23ff47afc8b7ea8631b3","tid":531513,"uid":98551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T06:00:28.000Z","msg":"No <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=